# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/app-office/lyx/ChangeLog,v 1.331 2015/04/08 07:30:33 mgorny Exp $

  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> lyx-2.0.8.1.ebuild,
  lyx-2.1.2.ebuild, lyx-2.1.3.ebuild:
  Remove old Python implementations

  30 Mar 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> lyx-2.1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #544700).

*lyx-2.1.3 (28 Feb 2015)

  28 Feb 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> -lyx-2.0.6.ebuild,
  -lyx-2.0.7.1-r2.ebuild, -lyx-2.1.1.ebuild, +lyx-2.1.3.ebuild:
  bump & drop old, fix bug 530726, 541532, thanks pavel

  06 Dec 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> lyx-2.1.2.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #529102

  04 Dec 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> lyx-2.1.2.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #529102

  03 Dec 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> lyx-2.1.2.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #529102

